Tyrael takes a good look at the two other leaders. He knew he could 
trust Rodimus and Tripredacus honor meant he wouldn't break his own 
word. What about Cygnar though? Time will tell, he thought.

Tyrael: So we agree on collaboration. To which extent do you want 
this, though? Simple non-agression pact or a deeper alliance?

It would always be good to have allies, especially since his was now a 
weak group, but he did not especially love the idea of sharing 
top-secret Tripred data with a band of rogue Predacons and nosy 
Maximals.
